dict.string: Inhale, and raise your arms above your head.
Exhale, spread your fingers, and hinge forward into a forward fold, placing hands on the mat.
Inhale, ground your hands, look up, and straighten your spine.
Exhale, float to the back of your mat, and come halfway down, elbows grazing the sides.
Inhale, roll onto the tops of your feet, opening the chest through straight arms, upward facing dog.
Exhale, tuck your toes and lift your hips and straighten your arms, downward facing dog.
Inhale, jump forward onto straight arms with legs bent in the air. Exhale, and bring legs through your arms and come to a seat.
Straighten your legs in front of you and sit up straight.
Inhale, grab your big toes, and straighten your back. On an exhale, hinge forward, bending your elbows so that your head reaches toward your toes.
Inhale, place your hands at your sides and lift up, bending legs in the air. Exhale, send your legs back and lower halfway down.
Inhale, roll on the tops of your feet and open your chest, upward facing dog.
Exhale, tuck your toes and push back to downward facing dog.
Look between your hands and jump your feet forward. Inhale, look up with a flat back.
Exhale and bring your chest towards your legs.
Inhale, look up with a straight spine.
Exhale, stand all the way up with hands at your sides.
